{"type": "article", "id": 5038, "title": "byAMT's Leather Strap Planter 花盆", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-08T08:04:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233628DoT56yAunLahEvJe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t在 2014 年的国际当代家具展(International Contemporary Furniture Fair)上，来自洛杉矶的 Mimot 设计工作室带来了一款可以提起来的花盆设计 byAMT's Leather Strap Planter 。随后，设计团队与 Cool Hunting 网站合作推出了一个绿色签名版本的环保花盆，采用植物鞣革与镀铜铆钉编织成一个手提篮子的形状，这样在你想给花花草草浇水或者让它们去晒太阳时，就不用搬来搬去，沾染上花盆边的泥土。定价 172 美元（约合人民币 1068 元），<a href=\"http://www.buyamt.com/collections/strap-collection/products/coolhunting-strap-planter-small\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233626UP4JLXfna8Gdyovk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233626VxEQ7uiPGwX42MsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233627fGkTmJcV8oh6uHqj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}